data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning, newly constructed residence, built in 2022, offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and spacious living.  With 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, and sprawling across 3,000 square feet, this home sits majestically on a generous 0.9-acre lot, providing you with  ample space both inside and out.  As you step inside, you'll immediately be captivated by the open concept floor plan, designed to enhance the flow of natural light and create a sense of  airiness throughout the home. The main level boasts a guest suite, providing convenience and privacy for your visitors or multigenerational living.  One of the highlights of this home is the third-level open loft, a versatile space that can serve as a home office for remote work,  or an entertainment area for hosting friends and family, bring your imagination. The possibilities are endless, and it's a unique feature that truly sets this home apart.  Outside, you'll discover your own private oasis. The expansive yard offers endless possibilities for gardening, recreation, or simply enjoying the serene  surroundings. Step onto the covered patio, where you can relax and entertain year-round, taking in the peaceful views of your lush backyard.  Additional features include high-quality construction, modern finishes, and attention to detail throughout the home. The 5 bedrooms provide ample  space for your family, guests, or a home gym. With 4 bathrooms, morning routines will be a breeze, and there will always be enough space for everyone.  This home offers the perfect balance of modern convenience, spacious living, and outdoor tranquility. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours.  Schedule a viewing today and start living the life you've always dreamed of in this 2022-built masterpiece! This home is USDA eligible and qualifies for  100% Financing.
